From: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>
Date: Tue, 9 Jun 2026 13:50:54 +0200
Subject: Revert "ALSA: timer: Fix UAF at snd_timer_user_params()"
Git-commit: dde75ff0f651182b671da700441406b8f9de3984
